.:: Zebra puzzle ::.
5 different games are played: snooker, backgammon, chess, billiard, mah-jongg
There are 5 different nationalities: english, spanish, ukranian, norwegian, japanese
5 different brands of cigars are smoked: old-gold, kools, chesterfields, lucky-strike, parliaments
The people have 5 different jobs:  dressmaker, manager, musician, chef, teacher
The people prefer 5 different music-genres: trance, r&b, punk, ambient, blues

1. the english is the person playing snooker
2. the spanish is the fan of trance
3. the dressmaker is the person playing backgammon
4. the ukranian is the manager
5. the person playing backgammon is to the right of the person playing chess
6. the old-gold-smoker is the fan of blues
7. the kools-smoker is the person playing billiard
8. the musician is in the middle
9. the norwegian is on the far left
10. the chesterfields-smoker is on the left or right of the fan of r&b
11. the kools-smoker is to the left or right of the fan of ambient
12. the lucky-strike-smoker is the chef
13. the japanese is the parliaments-smoker
14. the norwegian is to the left or right of the person playing mah-jongg

.:: Answer ::.
|		|       1	|	2	|	3 	|	4	|	5	|
| Nationality	|   norwegian	|    ukranian	|     english	|    spanish	|    japanese	|
| Game		|    billiard	|      mah-jongg	|      snooker	|     chess	|     backgammon	|
| Job	|     teacher	|      manager	|      musician	| chef	|     dressmaker	|
| Cigar		|     kools	| chesterfield	|    olg-gold	| lucky-strike	|   parliament	|
| Music-Genre		|     r&b	|     ambient	|     blues	|     trance	|     punk	|
